    "title": "京东开放平台不当使用关键词细则",
    "followRuleId": "1268110865350135808",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关键词混淆：指商家在商品信息（标题、详情页、广告等）中，故意使用与商品无真实关联的热门关键词，通过误导性表述吸引流量或提升转化，但实际商品不具备关键词所描述的特征、授权或功能，属于违规营销行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">品牌信息不一致：指在标题、宣传语、商品图片及商品详情等位置使用/滥用/堆砌其他品牌词（包括但不限于品牌的变形词或衍生词，如错别字、同音字、故意增加间隔符号等）来描述商品，与商品本身品牌不一致的行为。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></h1>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关键词混淆</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度轻微：警告；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度一般：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金500元；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违规商品近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元违约金（M3档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">品牌信息不一致</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度轻微：警告，违规商品屏蔽；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度一般：违规商品屏蔽、钱包资金冻结、<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">支付近14日全店商品销售额的10%作为违约金，最低100元，最高10,000元（M3档）</span> （实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度严重：店铺屏蔽、<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱包资金冻结、支付近14日全店商品销售额的20%作为违约金，最低300元，最高100,000元（M4档）</span> （实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度特别严重：店铺屏蔽、<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱包资金冻结、支付近14日全店商品销售额的30%作为违约金，最低500元，最高500,000元（M5档）</span> （实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如商家多次（两次及以上）或大量在售商品出现以上违规行为，或因上述行为引起重大投诉或舆情的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架、限制创建商品、店铺商品搜索/推荐降权、禁止上架待售商品、永久限制通过接口批量操作商品、限制在售商品阈值、限制提报营销活动、属性屏蔽、店铺屏蔽、商品屏蔽、品牌停用、类目停用、冻结资金、页面止付、降低店铺星级、跨类目经营限制、店铺清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1关键词混淆包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）非旗舰店商家宣传&ldquo;旗舰店&rdquo;等信息；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）商家在宣传中强行关联与商品无实际联系的知名IP、卖场、明星或影视作品，以不当获取流量。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2品牌信息不一致包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）挂靠品牌A，但在标题、主图等位置宣传除A以外其他品牌的相关信息；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）未挂靠品牌，但在商品信息里宣传与商品本身无关品牌信息。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.3<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台根据违规行为对用户体验造成的伤害程度，从轻到重执行M1到M7档位违约金，具体金额如下：</span> </span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.25pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.45pt; background: #dc1623; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 2;\" width=\"133\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13cm; background: #dc1623; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 2;\" width=\"491\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金标准</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.45pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"133\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害一级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0cm; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"491\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元及以下</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.45pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"133\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害二级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0cm; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"491\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">固定金额 200元/500元/800元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.45pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"133\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害三级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0cm; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"491\">\n<p style=\"text-align: ce